subject: RE: [junit] Re: Asserting Equality Of Collection Elements
msgSnippet: ... In addition, this test does not recursively apply to collections contained in the collection as the normal equal method will be used to test for
messageBody:
> Careful: this only checks "subcollection". You'd have to do it in each
> direction *and* check size *and* check elements appearing
> multiple times, to
> be sure.

In addition, this test does not recursively apply to collections contained
in the collection as the normal 'equal' method will be used to test for
existence. So, a shallow comparison is conducted.

David
